1
00:01:18,000 --> 00:01:19,599
Old Chen really called it right.

2
00:01:19,599 --> 00:01:21,560
There's a whole other world behind that ice wall.

3
00:01:42,000 --> 00:01:44,120
Finally out of that frozen wasteland.

4
00:01:44,599 --> 00:01:46,519
Look at all this green, it's so refreshing.

5
00:01:47,159 --> 00:01:48,879
A real paradise.

6
00:01:53,319 --> 00:01:54,159
Brother Chen.

7
00:01:54,480 --> 00:01:55,959
I think we're on the right path.

8
00:01:56,400 --> 00:01:57,599
From where we swam up,

9
00:01:58,120 --> 00:01:59,840
I think if we push forward along this path,

10
00:02:00,079 --> 00:02:01,519
we'll definitely make it out of the mountains.

11
00:02:01,719 --> 00:02:02,519
No.

12
00:02:02,519 --> 00:02:04,000
There's dense vegetation all around.

13
00:02:04,200 --> 00:02:05,959
Yet this path is unusually flat.

14
00:02:06,280 --> 00:02:08,840
I think it's been worn down by wild animals.

15
00:02:09,479 --> 00:02:10,360
Let's go that way.

16
00:02:11,719 --> 00:02:12,759
We'll head over there.

17
00:02:41,240 --> 00:02:43,080
Old Chen, look over there.

18
00:02:43,919 --> 00:02:45,479
Isn't that the giant eyeball?

19
00:02:46,680 --> 00:02:47,479
It really is!

20
00:02:48,240 --> 00:02:49,039
Miss He.

21
00:02:49,319 --> 00:02:51,360
Could that be the city of Mengna Valley?

22
00:02:52,039 --> 00:02:52,919
It must be.

23
00:02:53,719 --> 00:02:54,960
Past the Gate of Cataclysm,

24
00:02:55,039 --> 00:02:57,120
we should be in Mengna Valley territory.

25
00:02:57,360 --> 00:02:59,120
The long poem Dawang left me said

26
00:02:59,960 --> 00:03:02,280
Mengna Valley's capital is called Chimo Jizhou,

27
00:03:03,000 --> 00:03:04,719
shaped like a massive honeycomb.

28
00:03:05,800 --> 00:03:08,000
Nine times out of ten, this is the place.

29
00:03:08,080 --> 00:03:09,639
The Tower of Babel in ancient Babylon,

30
00:03:10,719 --> 00:03:12,960
the megaliths of Brittany,

31
00:03:13,360 --> 00:03:15,039
the 9,000-year-old

32
00:03:15,039 --> 00:03:16,560
golden city of Dwarka in Indian waters.

33
00:03:17,240 --> 00:03:18,439
In ancient civilizations,

34
00:03:18,479 --> 00:03:20,960
there are countless structures that defy imagination.

35
00:03:27,479 --> 00:03:28,599
There's no mistake.

36
00:03:28,960 --> 00:03:30,479
There's absolutely no mistake!

37
00:03:31,120 --> 00:03:32,319
Shaped like a honeycomb.

38
00:03:32,560 --> 00:03:33,759
Chimo Jizhou.

39
00:03:33,960 --> 00:03:35,599
It's truly magnificent!

40
00:03:36,479 --> 00:03:36,919
Wait...

41
00:03:36,919 --> 00:03:37,360
I...

42
00:03:37,919 --> 00:03:39,000
No, no, Uncle Min.

43
00:03:39,000 --> 00:03:40,240
Don't get yourself worked up.

44
00:03:40,240 --> 00:03:41,560
You'll give yourself a heart attack.

45
00:03:41,599 --> 00:03:42,240
Once that happens,

46
00:03:42,240 --> 00:03:44,080
your life's pursuit will be ruined.

47
00:03:44,159 --> 00:03:44,919
Brother Chen.

48
00:03:45,159 --> 00:03:45,800
Brother Chen.

49
00:03:45,960 --> 00:03:47,400
Chimo Jizhou is right here.

50
00:03:47,439 --> 00:03:48,360
I think there's no time to waste.

51
00:03:48,360 --> 00:03:49,520
Let's hurry inside.

52
00:03:50,039 --> 00:03:51,360
Rest, let's rest a bit.

53
00:03:51,439 --> 00:03:52,400
Just now under the ice tower,

54
00:03:52,400 --> 00:03:54,080
weren't you the one begging to rest?

55
00:03:54,439 --> 00:03:56,000
Fatty, you little punk!

56
00:03:56,319 --> 00:03:57,759
My lifelong pursuit

57
00:03:57,759 --> 00:03:59,199
is to find Mengna Valley,

58
00:03:59,360 --> 00:04:01,000
and uncover the secret of the Lingxiao Pearl.

59
00:04:01,479 --> 00:04:03,080
That is my lifelong pursuit.

60
00:04:03,479 --> 00:04:05,199
Now that it's right before my eyes,

61
00:04:05,360 --> 00:04:06,199
how can you expect me

62
00:04:06,759 --> 00:04:08,400
not to be anxious?

63
00:04:08,520 --> 00:04:10,639
Brother Chen, let's hurry inside.

64
00:04:13,439 --> 00:04:14,080
Let's go.

65
00:04:15,520 --> 00:04:16,720
Come on, come on.

66
00:04:18,079 --> 00:04:19,600
What's he rambling on about?

67
00:05:10,240 --> 00:05:10,839
Bi Huaqiang.

68
00:05:11,319 --> 00:05:11,959
Come here.

69
00:05:14,720 --> 00:05:16,639
Every time we got close to the Lingxiao Pearl before,

70
00:05:16,800 --> 00:05:18,920
your body had strange reactions.

71
00:05:19,560 --> 00:05:20,399
But every time

72
00:05:20,480 --> 00:05:22,279
when we thought we'd uncover the truth,

73
00:05:22,800 --> 00:05:24,680
we'd lose it at the last moment.

74
00:05:25,839 --> 00:05:27,040
So you're scared.

75
00:05:27,839 --> 00:05:29,600
You're afraid that once we reach Mengna Valley

76
00:05:29,759 --> 00:05:30,959
and find the Lingxiao Pearl,

77
00:05:31,720 --> 00:05:33,160
it'll all still come to nothing.

78
00:05:33,160 --> 00:05:34,399
The Lingxiao Pearl is tied to the lives

79
00:05:34,399 --> 00:05:35,439
of both Uncle Min and me.

80
00:05:35,879 --> 00:05:37,000
But whether we can break the curse,

81
00:05:37,000 --> 00:05:38,199
we have no idea.

82
00:05:38,680 --> 00:05:40,240
I've been thinking the whole way.

83
00:05:40,759 --> 00:05:42,759
From the ancient western city to Yunling,

84
00:05:42,839 --> 00:05:44,439
and from Yunling to Nanyun,

85
00:05:44,800 --> 00:05:46,600
the scale of the ruins along the way,

86
00:05:46,600 --> 00:05:47,800
the level of civilization,

87
00:05:47,879 --> 00:05:49,279
and the dangers we've faced

88
00:05:49,519 --> 00:05:51,360
have become increasingly unbelievable.

89
00:05:51,600 --> 00:05:52,399
So,

90
00:05:52,920 --> 00:05:54,279
you're thinking of backing out?

91
00:05:56,800 --> 00:05:58,879
I'll definitely finish this trip to Mengna Valley.

92
00:05:59,399 --> 00:06:00,720
No matter the outcome,

93
00:06:01,040 --> 00:06:02,720
I plan to bring my archaeology career

94
00:06:02,720 --> 00:06:03,720
to a close.

95
00:06:04,199 --> 00:06:05,800
As long as I, Chen Youxi, still draw breath

96
00:06:05,800 --> 00:06:06,959
and make it back alive,

97
00:06:07,839 --> 00:06:09,199
I want to stay by your side always.

98
00:06:25,399 --> 00:06:26,639
Quite spectacular.

99
00:06:27,879 --> 00:06:28,720
Beautiful.

100
00:06:31,360 --> 00:06:33,240
Good, it wasn't a wasted trip.

101
00:06:41,360 --> 00:06:42,279
Hey, Uncle Min,

102
00:06:42,560 --> 00:06:44,120
you usually grab your little stick

103
00:06:44,120 --> 00:06:45,879
and zip around pretty fast.

104
00:06:46,079 --> 00:06:47,360
Why'd you stop here?

105
00:06:47,920 --> 00:06:49,160
You fat oaf,

106
00:06:49,759 --> 00:06:50,959
asking the obvious.

107
00:06:53,639 --> 00:06:55,079
What's the big deal?

108
00:06:55,399 --> 00:06:56,920
It's six or seven meters at most,

109
00:06:56,920 --> 00:06:57,839
and it's not deep.

110
00:06:57,839 --> 00:06:59,519
Can't we just wade across?

111
00:07:00,399 --> 00:07:01,199
Wade across?

112
00:07:01,199 --> 00:07:02,399
Easier said than done.

113
00:07:03,319 --> 00:07:05,639
We nearly died getting out of that lake.

114
00:07:05,639 --> 00:07:06,959
And look at this water,

115
00:07:07,160 --> 00:07:08,160
it's filthy and murky.

116
00:07:08,160 --> 00:07:10,160
Who knows what monsters lurk inside.

117
00:07:10,600 --> 00:07:11,519
We can't get in the river,

118
00:07:11,920 --> 00:07:13,000
so let's find another way.

119
00:07:13,920 --> 00:07:15,040
In a city this big,

120
00:07:15,639 --> 00:07:17,120
there's got to be another route.

121
00:07:17,839 --> 00:07:19,519
Use your head, would you?

122
00:07:20,079 --> 00:07:20,959
Take a look.

123
00:07:21,600 --> 00:07:24,319
This was dug around the city on purpose.

124
00:07:25,040 --> 00:07:26,160
Do you know why?

125
00:07:26,240 --> 00:07:27,439
Precisely to keep out the likes of you,

126
00:07:27,439 --> 00:07:29,319
ignorant white-haired thieves.

127
00:07:29,519 --> 00:07:30,920
So Mengna Valley already had

128
00:07:30,920 --> 00:07:33,040
the concept of building a moat back then.

129
00:07:33,560 --> 00:07:35,839
This channel is pretty wide.

130
00:07:36,439 --> 00:07:37,959
You call this wide?

131
00:07:38,199 --> 00:07:40,839
You've never seen the moat in Xiangyang.

132
00:07:41,199 --> 00:07:41,920
Sister,

133
00:07:42,399 --> 00:07:44,639
to you this is a river.

134
00:07:45,120 --> 00:07:46,000
But to Fatty here,

135
00:07:46,680 --> 00:07:47,720
it's just a ditch.

136
00:07:48,399 --> 00:07:49,000
Right.

137
00:07:49,279 --> 00:07:50,639
Let Fatty here show you how it's done.

138
00:07:50,720 --> 00:07:52,120
Be careful.

139
00:07:58,360 --> 00:08:00,519
This, this is nothing, really.

140
00:08:01,000 --> 00:08:01,720
Honestly.

141
00:08:04,399 --> 00:08:05,120
Take it easy!

142
00:08:06,600 --> 00:08:07,680
What is it, Fatty?

143
00:08:08,800 --> 00:08:09,480
Nothing.

144
00:08:10,000 --> 00:08:10,879
Bah!

145
00:08:10,959 --> 00:08:13,800
Geez, my blood pressure nearly shot through the roof.

146
00:08:13,800 --> 00:08:14,600
Look at that.

147
00:08:20,199 --> 00:08:21,120
Now what?

148
00:08:21,480 --> 00:08:22,560
There's a whirlpool.

149
00:08:23,040 --> 00:08:23,959
A whirlpool?

150
00:08:24,879 --> 00:08:26,000
Are there icebergs in there?

151
00:08:26,600 --> 00:08:27,639
Any sharks?

152
00:08:27,759 --> 00:08:29,680
Crabs, ribbonfish, anything?

153
00:08:32,440 --> 00:08:34,080
Old Chen, help me!

154
00:08:34,080 --> 00:08:34,799
Fatty!

155
00:08:34,799 --> 00:08:35,759
What a faker.

156
00:08:35,759 --> 00:08:36,480
Fatty!

157
00:08:37,879 --> 00:08:39,519
Fatty! Catch!

158
00:08:43,039 --> 00:08:43,639
Here!

159
00:08:49,480 --> 00:08:50,919
It's a trap.

160
00:08:51,120 --> 00:08:53,200
Don't just stand there, go help him!

161
00:08:54,960 --> 00:08:56,360
Looks like a mechanism.

162
00:09:02,759 --> 00:09:04,679
You fat oaf, you're way too heavy.

163
00:09:04,960 --> 00:09:06,840
Eating less would have helped.

164
00:09:31,600 --> 00:09:33,200
Hurry up, pull harder!

165
00:09:34,639 --> 00:09:35,840
Why are they fighting now?

166
00:09:51,759 --> 00:09:53,039
Are you done yet?

167
00:09:54,480 --> 00:09:55,120
What's wrong?

168
00:09:55,200 --> 00:09:56,240
Brother Chen, you...

169
00:09:56,240 --> 00:09:58,000
Don't you know what your man's doing?

170
00:09:58,039 --> 00:09:58,840
My man?

171
00:10:01,559 --> 00:10:02,240
Bi Huaqiang!

172
00:10:02,600 --> 00:10:04,080
Bi Huaqiang, what are you doing?

173
00:10:04,399 --> 00:10:05,759
What's going on here?

174
00:10:07,519 --> 00:10:09,320
Did you think we're about to enter Mengna Valley

175
00:10:09,320 --> 00:10:10,240
and don't need us anymore?

176
00:10:10,240 --> 00:10:12,039
So you sent him to grab weapons and silence us?

177
00:10:12,120 --> 00:10:13,679
Bi Huaqiang, what happened?

178
00:10:13,679 --> 00:10:15,519
I honestly have no idea.

179
00:10:15,879 --> 00:10:17,679
I'm just as shocked he did this.

180
00:10:17,759 --> 00:10:18,960
If you don't believe me, ask An Xiang.

181
00:10:19,159 --> 00:10:20,120
Ask my ass!

182
00:10:20,399 --> 00:10:21,200
Old Chen...

183
00:10:24,399 --> 00:10:25,480
Why did you do it?

184
00:10:27,159 --> 00:10:28,399
Without a weapon in hand,

185
00:10:29,320 --> 00:10:30,440
I don't feel safe.

186
00:10:31,399 --> 00:10:32,480
Safe my ass!

187
00:10:32,480 --> 00:10:33,159
Godfather.

188
00:10:33,679 --> 00:10:34,320
Godfather!

189
00:10:35,200 --> 00:10:36,000
Godfather!

190
00:10:38,360 --> 00:10:40,399
You're good for nothing but ruining things!

191
00:10:41,120 --> 00:10:41,919
Here's how we'll do it.

192
00:10:42,039 --> 00:10:43,159
Bi Huaqiang stays here.

193
00:10:43,759 --> 00:10:44,960
You and An Xiang come with us.

194
00:10:47,320 --> 00:10:49,120
I think that's fair enough.

195
00:10:50,320 --> 00:10:51,360
This white-haired punk,

196
00:10:51,360 --> 00:10:52,720
we really can't bring him along.

197
00:10:53,000 --> 00:10:54,200
He'll just cause more trouble later.

198
00:10:54,200 --> 00:10:55,879
His temper's too rotten.

199
00:10:56,240 --> 00:10:57,919
Uncle Min, An Xiang...

200
00:10:58,279 --> 00:10:58,879
Look,

201
00:10:58,879 --> 00:11:01,159
Youxi has done right by us.

202
00:11:03,240 --> 00:11:05,000
But there's an undercurrent in the river.

203
00:11:05,000 --> 00:11:06,200
We can't cross either.

204
00:11:17,799 --> 00:11:18,679
Brother Chen...

205
00:11:18,679 --> 00:11:19,399
Shut up!

206
00:11:20,360 --> 00:11:21,039
Fatty,

207
00:11:21,240 --> 00:11:22,159
keep an eye on Whitey.

208
00:11:22,639 --> 00:11:23,240
Old Lu,

209
00:11:23,440 --> 00:11:24,240
find some wood to build a bridge.

210
00:11:24,480 --> 00:11:24,960
Got it.

211
00:11:38,000 --> 00:11:38,919
There!

212
00:12:00,360 --> 00:12:01,159
Just set it down.

213
00:12:05,679 --> 00:12:06,840
I'll go in and check first.

214
00:12:07,039 --> 00:12:07,679
Wait for my signal.

215
00:12:07,679 --> 00:12:08,320
Okay.

216
00:12:08,799 --> 00:12:09,519
Take it slow.

217
00:12:35,480 --> 00:12:36,159
Brother Chen!

218
00:12:36,519 --> 00:12:38,240
How... how's it looking over there?

219
00:12:38,600 --> 00:12:39,559
Quit rushing me!

220
00:12:40,000 --> 00:12:40,720
Hang on.

221
00:12:42,279 --> 00:12:43,080
It's safe!

222
00:12:58,399 --> 00:12:59,200
Nice!

223
00:13:26,120 --> 00:13:27,759
A trap!

224
00:13:33,480 --> 00:13:36,720
Brother Chen, are you kidding me?

